ned in the source, but that's not critical to include. The core information about which schema receives the data is captured in the knowledge file, so the omission of \"取引単体テスト等\" as a contextual example feels minor enough to overlook. I'll move forward without flagging this one.\n\nLooking at the section structure more carefully, I notice the \"ツールの特徴（設定ファイル不要）\" section is quite sparse compared to the source material—only one of three bullet points made it into this section while the others got distributed elsewhere. It's not a content problem per se, but the section itself ends up minimal. I don't think there are any critical issues to report here.\n\nThe only thing worth considering is whether the omission of \"取引単体テスト等\" from the main データ投入 description matters, but that's really just an example use case rather than essential decision-making information. The knowledge file accurately captures what schemas receive data, which is what matters. I'm marking this as clean.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":14616,"cache_read_input_tokens":18561,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":14616,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0d03cbb9-ec3e-4be7-85e3-e3502cb12b82","uuid":"07bf43c0-d9c6-4fcf-b0cf-4b9b21b6bafa"}
